OL,6,FA teacher who asked a former pupil to
OL,7,Fhave sex with him has been permanently
OL,8,Fstruck off.
OL,10,FNicholas Spink, from Wakefield,
OL,11,Fpropositioned the girl in a series of
OL,12,Fdrunken text messages in April 2020.
OL,14,FThe 42-year-old also asked her to send
OL,15,Fhim photos of herself.
OL,17,FFollowing a misconduct hearing Mr
OL,18,FSpink, who had been working at Outwood
OL,19,FAcademy City Fields at the time, was
OL,20,Fbarred from ever teaching again.
